org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel

Class HSSFPrintSetup

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel.HSSFPrintSetup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PrintSetup 

    public class HSSFPrintSetup
extends java.lang.Object
implements PrintSetup
    Used to modify the print setup.

    Paper size constants have been added for the ones I have access to. They follow as:
    public static final short PRINTER_DEFAULT_PAPERSIZE = 0;
    public static final short LETTER_PAPERSIZE = 1;
    public static final short LEGAL_PAPERSIZE = 5;
    public static final short EXECUTIVE_PAPERSIZE = 7;
    public static final short A4_PAPERSIZE = 9;
    public static final short A5_PAPERSIZE = 11;
    public static final short ENVELOPE_10_PAPERSIZE = 20;
    public static final short ENVELOPE_DL_PAPERSIZE = 27;
    public static final short ENVELOPE_CS_PAPERSIZE = 28;
    public static final short ENVELOPE_MONARCH_PAPERSIZE = 37;

    (用于修改打印设置。已为我可以访问的纸张添加了纸张大小常数。它们如下：公共静态最终短片PRINTER_Protect_PAPERISE = 0;公共静态最终短片LETTER_PAPERISE = 1;公共静态最终短片LEGAL_PAPERISE = 5;公共静态最终短片EXECUTIVE_PAPERISE = 7;公共静态最终短片A4_PAPERISE = 9;公共静态最终短片A5_PAPERISE = 11;公共静态最终短片ENVSEARCH PE_10_PAPERISE = 20; public static final short ENVINESS PE_DL_PAPERSIZE = 27; public static final short ENVINESS PE_CS_PAPERSIZE = 28; public static final short ENVINESS PE_MONELY_PAPERSIZE = 37;)
